Replace literal high-bit-set characters in regexp with escapes to avoid unicode hassle: if (text.match(/^-?[\xA2\xA3\xA5\u20A5\u20B9\u20AC\u20A1\u20B5\x24]?[\d,.]+%?$/)) or similar
Work when there are more then 256 rows

